<h4 id="sslpolicyprofile">Ssl<wbr>Policy<wbr>Profile</h4>

{{% choosable language csharp %}}
<dl class="tabular"><dt>Compatible</dt>
    <dd>COMPATIBLE{{% md %}}Compatible profile. Allows the broadset set of clients, even those which support only out-of-date SSL features to negotiate with the load balancer.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt>Custom</dt>
    <dd>CUSTOM{{% md %}}Custom profile. Allow only the set of allowed SSL features specified in the customFeatures field.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt>Modern</dt>
    <dd>MODERN{{% md %}}Modern profile. Supports a wide set of SSL features, allowing modern clients to negotiate SSL with the load balancer.{{% /md %}}</dd><dt>Restricted</dt>
    <dd>RESTRICTED{{% md %}}Restricted profile. Supports a reduced set of SSL features, intended to meet stricter compliance requirements.{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
